data.description: Waiting for you is this gorgeous home in the desired community of Silverwood. This home was built in 2021 and has many of the builder’s upgraded features. Beautifully tucked away on a manicured lot near the very private Everglades Nature Preserve area. Not to mention, the fabulous curb appeal from the paver driveway to the beautiful landscape. Step inside and into the contemporary open floor plan highlighted by soaring ceilings and tons of natural light. The spacious living and dining rooms open up effortlessly to a kitchen fitted with luxe granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances and beautiful large Island that’s comfortable to sit and eat. Upstairs, find all the bedrooms tucked away from the rest of the home for plenty of added privacy. By owning this home, you will also enjoy the Maple Ridge Reserve resort style clubhouse to include Community Park, Community Pool, Card Lounge, Craft Room, Playground, Dog Park, Tennis Courts, Walking Trials, Bike Paths, and Fitness Center. The schools are excellent and conveniently located near shopping and dining. Do not miss out on this wonderful opportunity.
